# ============================================================
# Root .dockerignore — governs the build context for every image
# built from the repo root (the 5 services + migrations + batch).
# Docker only reads a .dockerignore at the *context root*; since all
# these builds use `context: .`, this single file is authoritative.
# (The db/ image uses `context: ./db` and ships its own .dockerignore.)
#
# Goal: keep the daemon context small and free of secrets / VCS / caches.
# Anything excluded here is never sent to the Docker daemon, so it can
# neither bloat the build nor leak into a layer.
# ============================================================

# --- Version control & agent/editor metadata ---------------------------------
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github
.claude
.cursor
.vscode
.idea
.worktrees

# --- Secrets & local env (NEVER ship these into an image) --------------------
# Exclude every .env variant…
**/.env
**/.env.*
# …but keep the committed, secret-free templates so build-time tooling and
# documentation references resolve. The negation must come AFTER the broad rule.
!**/.env.example
!.env.prod.example
**/secrets/
**/*.pem
**/credentials.json

# --- Python caches & build artifacts -----------------------------------------
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pyo
**/.venv
**/venv
**/*.egg-info
**/dist
**/build
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.pytest_cache
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov

# --- Node / Expo client (never part of a backend image) ----------------------
**/node_modules
ratis_client

# --- Terraform / IaC state (may contain plaintext secrets) -------------------
**/.terraform
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*

# --- Documentation & local-only journals -------------------------------------
# Not needed at runtime. Keep the top-level README so an image that wants a
# project blurb (or a registry "source" link) still has it.
docs
**/*.md
!README.md

# --- Tests (not needed at runtime; --no-dev already skips their deps) ---------
**/tests
**/.tox

# --- Misc local noise --------------------------------------------------------
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
**/.ipynb_checkpoints
